===Etymology===
First attested in 1831. From {{etyl|de|en}} {{term|lang=de|Akkordeon}}, from {{term|Akkord||harmony|lang=de}}, from {{etyl|fr|en}} {{term|accord|lang=fr}}, from {{etyl|fro|en}} {{term|acorder|lang=fro}}, based on {{etyl|it|en}} {{term|lang=it|accordare||to tune}}. See also [[accord]].

